# Wavelet Matrix

[![CI](https://github.com/math-hiyoko/wavelet-matrix/actions/workflows/CI.yml/badge.svg?branch=main)](https://github.com/math-hiyoko/wavelet-matrix/actions/workflows/CI.yml)
